msgstr ":guilabel:`시작일`: 캘린더 선택기로 급여 공제가 적용될 날짜를 선택합니다."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/salary_attachments.rst:80
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Estimated End Date`: This field is **not** modifiable, and "
